Short Description
At Capgemini Portugal, we are searching for Data Engineers to reinforce our teams!
If you have at least 4 years of experience and you are looking for new challenges in Lisbon to help you evolve as a professional, Capgemini Portugal is the place for you!
What are we looking for?
Academic background in Computer Science or Engineering;
Fluent level of English;
Experience with GIT (bitbucket is a plus);
Professional experience with Python (mainly Pandas);

Are you passionate about Engineering?
